#### [MODIFY] [main_window.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/main_window.py)

- Rebalance grid weights for better proportions

## Verification

- Tab switch should be instant (no flicker)
- SearchableCombo dropdown should not flash
- Product tab config persists after restart
- Layout sections have visible separation
